  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb1\u0bb2\u0bcd, \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba4 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd - \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b9f \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "British High Commissioner-Presidential Special Discussion on Sri Lanka's Accountability, Human Rights",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Discussions were held between President Ranil Wickremesinghe and the British High Commissioner to Sri Lanka regarding Sri Lanka's accountability to United Nations human rights and compliance with human rights.",
        "Attention was paid to this matter during the meeting between President Ranil Wickremesinghe and British High Commissioner to Sri Lanka Sarah Halton on Thursday 28th.",
        "During this, High Commissioner Halton conveyed his greetings to the President and engaged in a detailed discussion on various issues.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe briefed the High Commissioner on the measures taken by the government for economic recovery and political stability.",
        "Various issues including Sri Lanka's accountability to United Nations human rights and compliance with human rights were also discussed here.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe stated that it is his wish to strengthen the relations between Sri Lanka and Britain and the High Commissioner promised full support for it.",
        "At the same time, the British High Commissioner posted on his Twitter page regarding this meeting, 'We expect to strengthen the relationship between Britain and Sri Lanka in a peaceful and democratic environment.",
        "This extensive discussion with the President emphasized the importance of human rights in Sri Lanka through the process of the United Nations Human Rights Council. mentioned that."
      ],
